Class FileChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileChecker

  • public class FileChecker
extends java.lang.Object
    class contains all the methods and fields to perform all the filter/select/outlier as well as compute methods, holds currentPerson, etc. to perform some methods, but takes data along with the stream
    Author:
    Jesse Zhong, jwz2111
    See Also:
